{
  "chapter": 23,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十三回描述了卜鹰、班察巴那和小方在沙漠中行进，遇到埋伏危险时，阳光突然出现接应他们。阳光如阳光般明朗活泼，与卜鹰有着深厚的情感联系。班察巴那在队伍即将到达拉萨时选择独自离开，展现了孤独的宿命。整章充满离别与重逢的情感，展现了沙漠中人物的坚韧与孤独。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "有人。前面的出口，两边山岩上都有人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "我们是退走？还是冲过去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "卜鹰，我想你，班察巴那，我想你，宋老头，我也想你。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "我好想你们。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "她姓蓝。她的名字就叫做阳光。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "可是我又想吓唬吓唬你们。可是我又不想把你们吓死。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "像你这样的人天下再也找不出第二个，万一，把你吓死了怎么办？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "你答应过我，这一次绝不出来乱跑的，为什么又跑出来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "你为什么总是喜欢捏我鼻子？是不是想把我的鼻子捏得像你一样？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "他是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "他叫小方。要命的小方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "为什么要叫他要命的小方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "因为有时候他跟你一样要命，有时候要把人气死，有时候想把人吓死。他自己却又偏偏是个不要命的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我喜欢不要命的男人。现在我已经开始有点喜欢你了！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我大哥的朋友就是我的朋友。他喜欢的人我都喜欢。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "我也喜欢你。真的很喜欢。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "你已经快到家了。我也该走了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "我知道。我回去，你走。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "他为什么不跟你回去？为什么要一个人走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为他天生就是个孤独的人，天生就喜欢孤独。他这一生中，大部分岁月都是在孤独中度过的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "你知道他要到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不知道。没有人知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "我不喜欢孤独。我们回家去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    }
  ],
